Breaking news on investment signals




Date
Type
Inside Scoop




2013-06-14
Project Scoop
Westport, CT – Networks. Bridgewater Associates, LP is currently planning to implement a network redesign, infrastructure upgrades, and new buildouts to its primarily Cisco-based network infrastructure in order to address issues including scalability, stability, and an increasingly complex network. Joseph McCartin is the Chief Information Officer (CIO). (Researched by Dorie Phillips)






